title: Temple of the Demon Oracle
story: Long after the Demon Oracle's death the temple remained uninhabited. Lately it was squatted by a party of thugs. Rumors say that untold treasures of ancient books are stored here.

notes.text: A mouth-shaped double door on the northern wall of the small room.
A sign on the wall: NO MORE DOOM
Remains of an elf apparently killed by elfs, a dagger and a map of the temple clutched in his hands.
A scarf in a broken trunk.
